// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2024-0292 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 8c83fc80-bcc6-527f-ac6b-ac72299346d9

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:8*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:9*")
